FORMAT:
1-category
2-name
3-information(in quotation marks)
4-media
5-OP(original poster)
6-date posted

MEDIA ORGANIZATION:
Put images/videos/files inside assets/info-sheets/category-name/ and put the file path on line 4.
Example media path: assets/info-sheets/weapons/acrodaggers.png
If there is no media, leave line 4 blank or type none.

